column5: Going to need to buy some ice in Vermillion Bay Saturday. Any suggestions? Thanks. Bill
the shell gas station/store where bobby's tackle shop is might be the best spot
Don't count on Bobby's for ice! We stopped there on Friday 9/3 at 6:30am on our way home & they had NO ICE!ðŸ¤¨. We got ice in Sioux Narrows.

I just called Bobby's, they have ice. The Co-op on Spruce St in Vermilion Bay also has ice.
